{"tid":2327354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機動部隊警員稱因社會運動遭友人孤立 情緒受困偷卡爆碌2.5萬買手機 認罪候判","createTime":"2020-12-16T04:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T05:43:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13daac9859c977318d38632756646395d43ab3a1","tid":2327354,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/ITKUS3KRAFGGFFPOPR77UXI7DQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FITKUS3KRAFGGFFPOPR77UXI7DQ%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=6a16eed3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FITKUS3KRAFGGFFPOPR77UXI7DQ%2F&h=4b90c373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/ITKUS3KRAFGGFFPOPR77UXI7DQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n被告警員李卓軒今早上庭，看來心情愉快。<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\n機動部隊警員聲稱去年社會運動期間，遭身邊友人孤立，情緒大受打擊。有次休班時，他在戲院取去別人遺下的信用卡，冒充卡主在戲院及銅鑼灣Apple Store瘋狂碌卡購物，包括購買兩部手提電話，涉款約2.5萬元。警員被控一項盜竊罪及兩項以欺騙手段取得財產罪，今早承認其中兩罪。裁判官張志偉將案件押後至本月30日，其間為被告索取社會服務令報告，涉案警員獲准保釋候判。"},{"pid":"f875004d75bd2b7488414995fef84f90a00a3798","tid":2327354,"uid":125235,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"偷嘢都咁多藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dd5ed77f519d31010aae603a88c0107918a794","tid":2327354,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:21:19.000Z","msg":"應該監都唔洗坐"},{"pid":"2630a586c1d0d336c2f67ed9e82a13785fa74b12","tid":2327354,"uid":366797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"如果佢只係停職冇停薪，梗係開心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}